data.description: This is a stunning property that offers modern comfort and style. The home features four spacious bedrooms, two full bathrooms and a powder room, and a full basement that awaits your finishing touches. The kitchen is a chef's dream with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a cozy breakfast nook. The family room is warm and inviting with a stack stone fireplace and hardwood floors. The master suite is located on the main level and boasts a tiled oversized shower. The home is situated in a gated community that provides access to a golf course, a lake, swimming pools, tennis courts, and many other amenities. The home sits on nearly ½ acre.  This is a rare opportunity to own a beautiful home in a desirable location.     MOTIVATED SELLER: Broker Bonus of $500 for accepted contract by 10-16-2023.
